Dust Wayne South died in Louisville, Kentucky, on Wednesday night . 
  Police were called to a field where South was seen waving a gun in the air . 
  Officers Rondall Carpenter and Zachary Cooke were involved in a shootout with South . 
  South was shot in the head but died at the scene . 
  Neighbors said he was fighting with a woman before police arrived . 
  Officers yelled at him to drop the gun but he pointed it at them and shot himself in the face . 
 